WEBVTT

00:01.701 --> 00:05.371
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

00:10.143 --> 00:13.645
Tao: PROVENZA,
IF YOU DON'T MIND.

00:13.647 --> 00:14.947
THANK YOU.

00:18.818 --> 00:20.119
SEVEN FEET.

00:20.820 --> 00:23.522
HOLD ONTO IT, PLEASE.
PLEASE. HOLD ON.

00:29.829 --> 00:32.064
GUY LIKED TO PARTY.

00:36.336 --> 00:40.205
WELL, LOOKED LIKE THE LAST TIME
THE VICTIM CHECKED HIS COMPUTER

00:40.207 --> 00:43.542
WAS AT 2:37 A.M.

00:51.518 --> 00:53.252
YOU CAN LET GO NOW.

00:54.921 --> 00:58.223
THE BULLET
DESCENDED 16 INCHES

00:58.225 --> 01:01.226
OVER A DOWNWARD TRAJECTORY
OF 2.26 DEGREES.

01:01.228 --> 01:04.063
Provenza: THAT WOULD PUT
THE SNIPER WHERE?

01:05.031 --> 01:06.765
CLEAN SHOT FROM THE ROOF

01:06.767 --> 01:10.035
OF THAT TALL BUILDING
ACROSS THE STREET, SIR.

01:10.037 --> 01:11.236
THAT COULD BE RIGHT.

01:11.238 --> 01:13.072
COULD BE?

01:13.074 --> 01:15.607
WELL, MY MEASUREMENTS
MIGHT BE OFF A LITTLE.

01:15.609 --> 01:17.109
ALL RIGHT.
SANCHEZ, GO OVER THERE

01:17.111 --> 01:20.779
AND SEE IF THE KILLER
LEFT ANYTHING BEHIND.

01:20.781 --> 01:23.115
SO, WHAT THE HECK
IS SWEET REVENGE, ANYWAY?

01:23.117 --> 01:25.417
OUR VICTIM, TRAVIS HALL,
RUNS A WEBSITE

01:25.419 --> 01:28.120
THAT LETS GUYS GET BACK
AT THEIR EX-GIRLFRIENDS

01:28.122 --> 01:30.055
BY POSTING NAKED PICTURES
OF THEM ONLINE.

01:30.057 --> 01:31.723
IT'S CALLED REVENGE PORN.

01:31.725 --> 01:34.026
WHATEVER HAPPENED TO
SCRIBBLING THE GIRL'S NAME

01:34.028 --> 01:35.227
ON A BATHROOM STALL?

01:35.229 --> 01:36.895
WELL, THIS SEEMS
TO PAY BETTER.

01:36.897 --> 01:38.263
AND THE VICTIM'S ASSISTANT

01:38.265 --> 01:39.965
TOLD PATROL
HE ARRIVED THIS MORNING

01:39.967 --> 01:41.967
AND FOUND HIS BOSS MURDERED
AND HIMSELF OUT OF A JOB.

01:41.969 --> 01:43.235
HIS ALIBI'S GOOD.

01:43.237 --> 01:45.237
ANY REASON WHY HIS BOSS

01:45.239 --> 01:47.306
WOULD BE UP IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT ON HIS COMPUTER?

01:47.308 --> 01:51.276
WHY ARE MEN EVER UP LATE
AT NIGHT ON THEIR COMPUTERS?

01:52.579 --> 01:54.580
ALSO, ACCORDING TO NEIGHBORS,

01:54.582 --> 01:57.583
HALL HAD A LOT OF GIRLFRIENDS
WHO CAME AND WENT AT ALL HOURS.

01:57.585 --> 01:59.384
THE LOCK ON THE DOOR
IS A KEYPAD.

01:59.386 --> 02:01.920
I WONDER HOW MANY OF HIS
GIRLFRIENDS HAD THE CODE?

02:01.922 --> 02:05.624
ARE YOU TELLING ME THAT WOMEN
WERE INTERESTED IN THIS CREEP?

02:05.626 --> 02:07.726
SEE?
YOU SHOULD NEVER GIVE UP.

02:09.462 --> 02:11.396
Buzz: OH, GOD.

02:11.398 --> 02:13.465
COME READ SOME OF THESE LETTERS
ON THE VICTIM'S BULLETIN BOARD.

02:13.467 --> 02:15.300
Sykes: "THESE PHOTOS
HAVE RUINED MY LIFE.

02:15.302 --> 02:17.136
"I'LL DO ANYTHING
IF YOU TAKE THEM DOWN."

02:17.138 --> 02:18.770
Buzz:
LOOK WHAT HE WROTE UNDERNEATH.

02:18.772 --> 02:20.172
"YOU'LL DO ANYTHING?

02:20.174 --> 02:22.107
TOO LATE, DUMB BITCH.
ENJOY YOUR PAIN."

02:22.109 --> 02:24.276
HE PUT THIS STUFF UP
LIKE HE WAS PROUD OF IT.

02:24.278 --> 02:27.346
EVERYONE WHO WROTE THIS GUY
IS A POTENTIAL SUSPECT.

02:27.348 --> 02:30.182
ALL RIGHT, LET'S TAKE IT ALL
WITH US, DAMN IT.

02:30.184 --> 02:31.950
OH, LOOK AT THIS --

02:31.952 --> 02:35.754
AN FBI WARRANT
FROM SIX WEEKS AGO.

02:35.756 --> 02:38.957
[ SCOFFS ]
WE'VE ONLY BEEN HERE AN HOUR

02:38.959 --> 02:40.926
AND WE'VE ALREADY CAUGHT UP
WITH THEM, YOU KNOW?

02:40.928 --> 02:43.962
MAYBE ALL THIS CAN BE
THEIR PROBLEM.

02:43.964 --> 02:45.664
[ POLICE RADIO CHATTER ]

02:45.666 --> 02:47.199
I FOUND A BULLET.

02:47.201 --> 02:49.468
AND IT'S FROM A LONG RIFLE,

02:49.470 --> 02:52.971
SO MAYBE A SNIPER
FROM ACROSS THE STREET.

02:52.973 --> 02:54.306
LIKE EVERYONE SAID.

02:54.308 --> 02:57.142
AH, YES.
THANK YOU FOR PICKING UP.

02:57.144 --> 02:59.111
AND HOW ARE YOU
THIS MORNING,

02:59.113 --> 03:01.213
VERY SPECIAL AGENT
FRITZ HOWARD?

03:01.215 --> 03:03.715
MY NECK IS KILLING ME,
AND MY SHOULDER.

03:03.717 --> 03:05.684
MY ARM, TOO.

03:05.686 --> 03:08.020
DID YOU HURT YOURSELF?
I DON'T THINK SO.

03:08.022 --> 03:10.355
I'VE BEEN BENT OVER BOX
AFTER BOX OF INVENTORY

03:10.357 --> 03:11.657
I HAVE TO LABEL

03:11.659 --> 03:13.992
BEFORE OFFICIALLY RETIRING
FROM THE FBI.

03:13.994 --> 03:15.561
ALSO, MOVING EVERYTHING
FROM WILSHIRE

03:15.563 --> 03:18.397
TO THE SPECIAL OPERATIONS
BUREAU, THAT WAS HARD.

03:18.399 --> 03:20.999
I'M A LITTLE STRESSED OUT
ABOUT BEING A BOSS.

03:21.001 --> 03:22.367
Sharon: YOU'LL ADAPT.

03:22.369 --> 03:24.803
DEPUTY CHIEF HOWARD
HAS A NICE RING TO IT.

03:24.805 --> 03:26.004
THANKS.

03:26.006 --> 03:27.573
IT'S GONNA BE
AN INTERESTING CHANGE.

03:27.575 --> 03:29.208
MM.
BRENDA ENDS UP
TAKING THIS JOB

03:29.210 --> 03:30.809
SHE'S BEEN MEETING ON
IN WASHINGTON,

03:30.811 --> 03:32.844
THE WHOLE THING COULD BE
A BIT OF A JUGGLING ACT.

03:32.846 --> 03:34.179
BUT I THINK
WE CAN HANDLE IT.

03:34.181 --> 03:35.814
OH, SHARON.
SHARON.

03:35.816 --> 03:37.983
I'LL MEET YOU THERE,
SHARON.

03:37.985 --> 03:39.985
HEY, LOOK,
I-I CANNOT PICK UP RICKY

03:39.987 --> 03:42.421
AT THE AIRPORT BY MYSELF.
I BARELY KNOW HIM.

03:42.423 --> 03:44.723
AND -- AND HE DOES NOT
LIKE ME VERY MUCH.

03:44.725 --> 03:46.225
WHY WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

03:46.227 --> 03:49.361
WELL, BECAUSE EVER SINCE
YOU STARTED DIVORCING JACK,

03:49.363 --> 03:52.197
HE'S BEEN, LIKE,
REALLY DISTANT ON THE PHONE.

03:52.199 --> 03:56.602
RUSTY, YOU AND RICKY
ARE GOING TO BE BROTHERS.

03:56.604 --> 03:59.104
PICKING EACH OTHER UP
AT THE AIRPORT

03:59.106 --> 04:00.539
IS WHAT FAMILIES DO.

04:00.541 --> 04:03.108
IT'LL BE FINE.
DON'T WORRY.

04:03.110 --> 04:04.576
Travis: <i>IT'S NOT MY FAULT</i>
<i>THEY'RE EMBARRASSED</i>
<i>OF THEMSELVES.</i>

04:04.578 --> 04:06.178
<i>I WASN'T THERE</i>
<i>WHEN THEY UNDRESSED,</i>

04:06.180 --> 04:08.614
<i>AND I DIDN'T PAY ANYONE</i>
<i>TO SNAP THE PHOTOS.</i>

04:08.616 --> 04:10.816
<i>HOW IS IT MY FAULT?</i>

04:12.252 --> 04:16.521
OUR INVESTIGATION CONCLUDED
THAT SWEET REVENGE ONLINE

04:16.523 --> 04:18.690
NETS OVER $10 MILLION A YEAR.

04:18.692 --> 04:22.094
HOW COME THE BUREAU HASN'T
ALREADY SHUT DOWN THIS WEBSITE?

04:22.096 --> 04:26.365
UNFORTUNATELY, LEGALLY,
IT'S PROTECTED SPEECH.

04:26.367 --> 04:29.101
WOMEN HAVE BEEN PHYSICALLY
THREATENED BY MR. HALL.

04:29.103 --> 04:31.570
THAT'S A VIOLATION
OF CALIFORNIA LAW, TOO.
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.

04:31.572 --> 04:33.138
WE DIDN'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT THAT UNTIL TODAY.
I COULD JUST AS EASILY ASK,

04:33.140 --> 04:34.640
"WHY DIDN'T THE L.A.P.D.
DO ANYTHING?"

04:34.642 --> 04:36.608
IF THE FBI HAD PASSED
THIS INFORMATION ALONG --

04:36.610 --> 04:38.744
WE FOLLOWED THE MONEY,
HOPING TO SHUT DOWN THE SITE

04:38.746 --> 04:40.379
BY IDENTIFYING FRAUD
OR RACKETEERING.

04:40.381 --> 04:42.281
THE PICTURES THEMSELVES
DON'T HELP US.

04:42.283 --> 04:44.950
WHAT IF THESE PHOTOGRAPHS
WERE OBTAINED ILLEGALLY?

04:44.952 --> 04:46.952
WE NEEDED EVIDENCE
OF EITHER THEFT OR HACKING.

04:46.954 --> 04:48.720
WE COULD NEVER GET IT.

04:48.722 --> 04:51.723
MURDER GIVES THE L.A.P.D.
BETTER GROUNDS FOR A WARRANT.

04:51.725 --> 04:54.426
YOU SAID SWEET REVENGE
NETTED $10 MILLION A YEAR.

04:54.428 --> 04:57.229
HOW MUCH OF THAT WENT
TO THIS TRAVIS HALL DIRTBAG?

04:57.231 --> 04:58.597
LESS THAN 5%.

04:58.599 --> 05:00.632
NO, HALL'S JUST
THE, UH, FRONT MAN.

05:00.634 --> 05:03.468
KEY PLAYER IS A GUY
NAMED SCOTT WARD,

05:03.470 --> 05:05.604
WHO, UH, MAY BE
A LITTLE MOBBED UP.

05:05.606 --> 05:08.573
WE'VE INVITED MR. WARD OVER
FOR A CHAT.

05:08.575 --> 05:10.575
HE'S COMING WITH HIS LAWYER.

05:10.577 --> 05:13.245
ALAN BURKE.
TERRIBLE GUY.

05:13.247 --> 05:17.115
REGARDLESS, A SNIPER ATTACK
MIGHT MAKE MR. WARD FEEL

05:17.117 --> 05:20.585
THAT HIS OWN SAFETY
REQUIRES HIM TO COOPERATE.

05:20.587 --> 05:22.187
I'D BE HAPPY TO HELP
WITH THAT INTERVIEW.

05:22.189 --> 05:24.656
BETTER USE MY FBI CONNECTIONS
WHILE YOU STILL CAN.

05:27.994 --> 05:29.795
Burke: IS THIS THREAT
TO MY CLIENT?

05:29.797 --> 05:32.030
'CAUSE WE CAME DOWN HERE
UNDER THE ASSUMPTION

05:32.032 --> 05:33.799
WE'D BE HELPING YOU
FIND A KILLER,

05:33.801 --> 05:34.933
NOT SUBMIT INFORMATION
ABOUT MY CLIENT'S

05:34.935 --> 05:36.668
LEGITIMATE
BUSINESS ACTIVITIES.

05:36.670 --> 05:39.438
THE L.A.P.D. THINKS THESE
LEGITIMATE BUSINESS ACTIVITIES

05:39.440 --> 05:41.606
MIGHT BE A LEGITIMATE MOTIVE
FOR MURDER.

05:41.608 --> 05:44.443
Flynn: THE SNIPER WHO KILLED
YOUR PARTNER,

05:44.445 --> 05:46.645
HE MIGHT JUST HAVE YOU IN
THE CROSS HAIRS TOO, MR. WARD.

05:46.647 --> 05:48.046
OKAY, FIRST, TRAVIS AND I
WERE NOT PARTNERS.

05:48.048 --> 05:49.681
SCOTT, THESE ARE BLATANT
INTIMIDATION TECHNIQUES.

05:49.683 --> 05:51.283
I'M NOT INTIMIDATED, ALAN.
I'M FREAKED OUT.

05:51.285 --> 05:53.919
OKAY? THE L.A.P.D.
DIDN'T KILL TRAVIS, OKAY?

05:55.021 --> 05:56.788
LOOK, HE MIGHT HAVE BEEN
THE PERFECT PERSON

05:56.790 --> 05:59.458
TO PROMOTE SWEET REVENGE,
BUT THE WEBSITE WAS MY IDEA,

05:59.460 --> 06:02.027
PUT TOGETHER WITH MY INVESTORS
AND MY SERVERS.

06:02.029 --> 06:05.464
SO IF PEOPLE CONNECTED TO IT
ARE GETTING KILLED...

06:05.466 --> 06:06.865
<i>GOD.</i>

06:06.867 --> 06:08.367
<i>SAME WAY</i>
<i>WITH TRAVIS' WEBSITE...</i>

06:08.369 --> 06:11.303
ANY LIKELY SUSPECTS
AMONG THE LETTER WRITERS?

06:11.305 --> 06:14.172
HOW ABOUT ALL OF THEM?
AND THEIR FATHERS, TOO.

06:14.174 --> 06:15.807
I'M TELLING YOU, CAPTAIN,

06:15.809 --> 06:18.410
THIS SCOTT WARD GUY'S NOT
GONNA HANG AROUND HERE FOREVER.

06:18.412 --> 06:20.712
WHAT IS TAKING TAO
SO LONG?

06:20.714 --> 06:22.647
NO ONE ELSE COULD GET THIS DONE
AS FAST AS MIKE.

06:22.649 --> 06:24.216
WE JUST NEED TO HOLD ON.

06:24.218 --> 06:26.485
OKAY, FOR CENTURIES,
WOMEN HAVE BEEN DUMPING MEN

06:26.487 --> 06:27.719
WITHOUT A SECOND THOUGHT.

06:27.721 --> 06:29.154
WE'RE PUTTING A BIG DENT
IN THAT PATTERN.

06:29.156 --> 06:30.822
AND THE WORLD'S
A BETTER PLACE FOR IT.

06:30.824 --> 06:33.024
Flynn: WELL, CONSIDERING
YOU'RE PROVIDING THE PLANET

06:33.026 --> 06:35.327
WITH SUCH A NOBLE
PUBLIC SERVICE,

06:35.329 --> 06:37.229
HOW COME YOU STAYED
OUT OF THE SPOTLIGHT

06:37.231 --> 06:39.331
AND LET YOUR FRIEND TRAVIS
TAKE ALL THE BOWS?

06:39.333 --> 06:42.167
ANYTHING TO DO WITH ALL
THESE THREATENING LETTERS?

06:42.169 --> 06:44.536
Burke: <i>SUCCESSFUL BUSINESSES</i>
<i>ATTRACT COMPLAINTS.</i>

06:44.538 --> 06:45.871
I HAVE IT.
INTERVIEW 1.

06:45.873 --> 06:47.739
<i>...WE'RE NOT CONCERNED</i>
<i>ABOUT IT.</i>

06:47.741 --> 06:50.075
Scott: <i>BESIDES, YOU SAID YOU</i>
<i>WERE LOOKING FOR A SNIPER.</i>

06:50.077 --> 06:51.410
<i>I MEAN, DO YOU REALLY</i>
<i>THINK A WOMAN COULD DO</i>
<i>SOMETHING LIKE THIS?</i>

06:51.412 --> 06:53.512
I THINK THERE COULD BE
A LINE OF THEM.

06:53.514 --> 06:55.247
LOOK,
MY CLIENT WARNED TRAVIS

06:55.249 --> 06:57.282
ABOUT HANGING OUT
WITH DRUG DEALERS,

06:57.284 --> 06:59.684
NOT TO MENTION ALL THE HOOKERS
HE HAD OVER.

06:59.686 --> 07:02.521
THIS TRAGEDY IS MORE
ABOUT TRAVIS' LIFESTYLE

07:02.523 --> 07:04.856
THAN IT IS
ABOUT SCOTT'S BUSINESS.

07:05.892 --> 07:08.193
UH-HUH.

07:08.195 --> 07:11.229
WELL, MAYBE AFTER THE FBI
AND THE L.A.P.D.

07:11.231 --> 07:12.697
GET A GOOD LOOK
AT YOUR CLIENT'S SERVERS,

07:12.699 --> 07:14.433
WE'LL AGREE WITH YOU.

07:14.435 --> 07:16.101
NICE TRY.
BUT UNLESS YOU HAVE EVIDENCE

07:16.103 --> 07:17.769
OF MONEY LAUNDERING
OR RACKETEERING,

07:17.771 --> 07:19.371
FEDERAL GOVERNMENT'S
NOT GOING ANYWHERE NEAR

07:19.373 --> 07:20.705
MY CLIENT'S SERVERS.

07:20.707 --> 07:22.707
Flynn: THIS IS NOT ABOUT
DOUBLE-CHECKING

07:22.709 --> 07:26.044
YOUR BOOKKEEPING ANYMORE.
THIS IS ABOUT MURDER.

07:26.046 --> 07:28.046
THE JUDGE JUST SIGNED A WARRANT
GRANTING US PERMISSION

07:28.048 --> 07:30.382
TO SEARCH THROUGH
ALL YOUR DATA.

07:30.384 --> 07:32.384
SO IF YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHO KILLED TRAVIS,

07:32.386 --> 07:34.319
NOW IS A PERFECT TIME.
YOU KNOW WHAT?
YOU WERE NEVER INTERESTED

07:34.321 --> 07:36.054
IN HAVING US HELP YOU
IDENTIFY SUSPECTS.

07:36.056 --> 07:37.789
YOU KNOW, ALAN, I THINK --
ALAN, WE SHOULD JUST PRO--

07:37.791 --> 07:39.424
NO. YOU, SCOTT, YOU'RE
NOT TALKING ANYMORE.

07:39.426 --> 07:42.527
YOU ARE COMING WITH ME...
NOW.

07:45.298 --> 07:47.098
HEY, SCOTTY.

07:47.100 --> 07:50.435
YOU DON'T WANT TO HELP US,
LET ME GIVE YOU SOME ADVICE --

07:50.437 --> 07:52.270
STAY AWAY FROM WINDOWS.

07:52.272 --> 07:53.972
SCOTT.

08:00.346 --> 08:01.913
I HATE TO SAY IT, CAPTAIN,

08:01.915 --> 08:03.515
<i>BUT I THINK WE NEED</i>
<i>TO KEEP AN EYE</i>

08:03.517 --> 08:05.116
<i>ON SCOTT WARD,</i>
<i>FOR SAFETY'S SAKE.</i>

08:05.118 --> 08:07.452
AGREED.
LET'S GET AMY ON THAT.

08:07.454 --> 08:11.156
AND ROLL OUT S.I.S.
SHE'S GONNA NEED BACKUP.

08:15.127 --> 08:17.762
SYKES.
LIEUTENANT.

08:17.764 --> 08:19.764
TALKING TO THE PEOPLE
WHO WROTE LETTERS.

08:19.766 --> 08:21.132
I HAVE A SUSPECT.

08:21.134 --> 08:23.935
THAT'S HIM, KEITH PRICE.
EX-ARMY RANGER.

08:23.937 --> 08:27.005
AFTER HIS WIFE'S PICTURES
GOT POSTED, SHE KILLED HERSELF.

08:27.007 --> 08:28.607
WELL, THAT'S GOOD MOTIVE.

08:28.609 --> 08:31.309
AND ARMY RANGERS HAVE
MANDATORY SNIPER TRAINING.

08:31.311 --> 08:34.446
AND CAN HIDE IN PLAIN SIGHT
WITHOUT LEAVING A TRACE BEHIND.

08:34.448 --> 08:36.681
Tao: ALL RIGHT. BEFORE
WE TURN DOWN SNIPER ALLEY,

08:36.683 --> 08:38.283
I'D LIKE TO CHECK
MY MEASUREMENTS

08:38.285 --> 08:39.518
AGAINST THE AUTOPSY,
IN CASE I MISSED SOMETHING.

08:39.520 --> 08:40.685
ALL RIGHT.

08:40.687 --> 08:43.622
Ricky: HI, MOM.
[ GASPS ]

08:43.624 --> 08:44.856
RICKY!

08:44.858 --> 08:46.157
HI!
HI!

08:46.159 --> 08:48.627
OH!
OH, MY GOSH.

08:48.629 --> 08:51.463
LOOK AT YOU. OH, MY GOSH.
WHAT IS THIS?

08:51.465 --> 08:53.198
GOT A LITTLE SCRUFF.
IT'S CUTE.
THANK YOU.

08:53.200 --> 08:55.667
UH...BOY, YOU GUYS
GOT BACK HERE QUICKLY.

08:55.669 --> 08:57.235
YEAH.
WELL, UH, RUSTY'S --

08:57.237 --> 08:59.804
HE KNOWS HIS WAY
AROUND THE BIG CITY.
YEAH.

08:59.806 --> 09:02.007
I ALSO KNOW HOW
TO TAKE DIRECTIONS WELL.

09:02.009 --> 09:03.742
LIEUTENANT, DO YOU
REMEMBER MY SON RICKY?

09:03.744 --> 09:05.243
HEY.
HOW ARE YOU, RICKY?

09:05.245 --> 09:06.711
GOOD TO SEE YOU AGAIN.
CAPTAIN.
YEAH?

09:06.713 --> 09:11.483
UM...WE'RE GOING TO,
UH, HOLD OUR EX-RANGER

09:11.485 --> 09:14.152
UNTIL WE CAN RUN A BACKGROUND
CHECK ON HIM, OKAY?

09:14.154 --> 09:17.322
UM, WHY DON'T WE GO
INTO MY OFFICE FOR A MOMENT?

09:17.324 --> 09:19.824
SURE.
RUSTY, YOU TOO.
COME ON.

09:35.007 --> 09:36.575
WELL, MY BIGGEST NEWS

09:36.577 --> 09:38.176
IS THAT WE'RE NOT PLANNING
ON GOING PUBLIC ANYMORE

09:38.178 --> 09:40.245
BECAUSE A LARGER
INTERNET-SECURITY FIRM

09:40.247 --> 09:41.346
OFFERED US A BUYOUT.

09:41.348 --> 09:42.781
AW, DOES THAT MEAN

09:42.783 --> 09:44.616
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO WORK
FOR SOMEONE ELSE?

09:44.618 --> 09:46.284
I DON'T KNOW.

09:46.286 --> 09:48.053
MAYBE I'LL JUST, YOU KNOW,
TAKE THE CASH AND TRAVEL.

09:48.055 --> 09:50.121
AND I HAVEN'T REALLY STOPPED
SINCE COLLEGE, RIGHT?

09:50.123 --> 09:52.123
AND A HOUSE AND A CAR
ONLY TIE YOU DOWN.

09:52.125 --> 09:53.525
RIGHT, RUSTY?

09:53.527 --> 09:54.960
OH, I DON'T KNOW.

09:54.962 --> 09:56.628
I'VE NEVER REALLY THOUGHT
ABOUT THAT BEFORE.

09:56.630 --> 09:58.229
WELL, YOU DON'T HAVE TO,
I GUESS.

09:58.231 --> 10:01.066
AND I'D, UH, I'D LIKE TO SPEND
MORE TIME IN L.A.

10:01.068 --> 10:02.567
WHAT?
YEAH, YEAH.

10:02.569 --> 10:04.202
I WANT TO TAKE YOU OUT
FOR DINNER TONIGHT, MOM,

10:04.204 --> 10:06.071
AND WE COULD, YOU KNOW, TALK
ABOUT THE FUTURE A LITTLE.

10:06.073 --> 10:09.541
I DON'T THINK I'M GOING
TO GET OUT OF HERE FOR DINNER.

10:09.543 --> 10:11.042
YOU'RE WORKING TONIGHT?

10:11.044 --> 10:12.577
MOM, I JUST GOT
OFF THE PLANE.

10:12.579 --> 10:14.579
I THOUGHT WE WERE GONNA
SPEND SOME TIME TOGETHER.

10:14.581 --> 10:17.148
I KNOW. I AM SO SORRY.

10:17.150 --> 10:19.317
I HAVE A SNIPER PROBLEM.

10:19.319 --> 10:22.887
UH, MAYBE YOU AND RUSTY
COULD GRAB A BITE TO EAT,

10:22.889 --> 10:26.324
AND THEN WE CAN HAVE BREAKFAST
TOGETHER TOMORROW, I HOPE.

10:26.326 --> 10:27.993
I'M SORRY.
I'M...

10:27.995 --> 10:29.694
Ricky: YEAH.
OKAY.

10:32.732 --> 10:34.899
L-LET ME JUST GRAB MY STUFF,
AND THEN I'LL RUN YOU HOME.

10:38.604 --> 10:41.272
OKAY, WHEN S.I.D. PULLED
ALL THIS CRAP OFFLINE,

10:41.274 --> 10:42.674
INSTEAD OF SHUTTING DOWN,

10:42.676 --> 10:45.410
THE WEBSITE SWITCHED OVER
TO SOMETHING CALLED --

10:45.412 --> 10:47.178
Ricky:
MIRROR SERVERS?

10:47.180 --> 10:49.914
YEAH. HEY, RICKY.
ANDY.

10:49.916 --> 10:51.282
THE DATA
WILL STILL BE INTACT,

10:51.284 --> 10:52.684
BUT YOU'RE GONNA
NEED SOME HELP

10:52.686 --> 10:53.952
GETTING THROUGH
THEIR FIREWALLS.

10:53.954 --> 10:55.153
WHERE'S LIEUTENANT TAO?

10:55.155 --> 10:56.621
Provenza:
OH, HE'S AT THE MORGUE

10:56.623 --> 10:58.189
OBSESSING OVER
BULLET TRAJECTORIES.

10:58.191 --> 10:59.524
WELL, MOM,
THESE ARE MOST LIKELY

10:59.526 --> 11:00.992
LOAD-BALANCED SERVERS
RUNNING APACHE...

11:00.994 --> 11:02.427
HI.

11:02.429 --> 11:04.496
...OR, UH, MAYBE
FEDORA UNDER LINUX.

11:04.498 --> 11:07.465
NOTHING ADVANCED -- I COULD
PROBABLY GET THESE BOOTED UP

11:07.467 --> 11:09.200
AND RESET
THE ROOT PASSWORDS.

11:09.202 --> 11:11.936
DO YOU GUYS HAVE SOMEPLACE
I COULD PLUG THIS STUFF IN?

11:17.143 --> 11:18.877
OH, I'M SORRY.

11:23.049 --> 11:25.483
OH, I DON'T --
I DON'T REALLY NEED YOU GUYS.

11:25.485 --> 11:28.186
I KNOW, HONEY, BUT WE HAVE
CHAIN-OF-CUSTODY ISSUES,

11:28.188 --> 11:30.889
AND YOU'RE NOT
AN OFFICER OF THE COURT.
GOTCHA.

11:30.891 --> 11:32.624
AND I'LL JUST STAY
OUT OF YOUR WAY.

11:32.626 --> 11:34.392
THANKS. SORRY
TO INVADE YOUR SPACE.

11:35.561 --> 11:36.895
TURNABOUT IS FAIR PLAY,
RIGHT?

11:36.897 --> 11:39.831
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

11:39.833 --> 11:42.634
I -- I'LL JUST WAIT
IN THE BREAK ROOM.

11:43.669 --> 11:45.970
OUR ARMY RANGER
HAS BEEN READ HIS RIGHTS

11:45.972 --> 11:48.306
AND HAS AGREED
TO COOPERATE.
THANK YOU.

11:48.308 --> 11:49.574
Flynn: DON'T WORRY.

11:49.576 --> 11:51.342
WE'LL KEEP AN EYE
ON DR. EINSTEIN HERE

11:51.344 --> 11:52.977
UNTIL MIKE GETS BACK.

11:52.979 --> 11:54.713
JUST DON'T LET YOUR SUSPECT
CONFESS BEFORE I GET A CHANCE

11:54.715 --> 11:56.648
TO LOOK AT SWEET REVENGE
ONLINE'S FINANCES.

11:56.650 --> 12:00.218
MM.
UM, LIEUTENANT, IF I GO LONG,

12:00.220 --> 12:01.953
WILL YOU CHECK
ON MIKE'S PROGRESS?

12:05.725 --> 12:08.760
<i>ALL RANGERS SPECIALIZE</i>
<i>IN FIREARMS.</i>

12:08.762 --> 12:11.162
<i>UH, SORRY TO INTERRUPT.</i>

12:11.164 --> 12:13.431
<i>CAPTAIN SHARON RAYDOR.</i>

12:13.433 --> 12:16.701
UM, THANK YOU, LIEUTENANT PRICE
<i>FOR AGREEING TO COOPERATE...</i>

12:16.703 --> 12:19.504
HOW'S TAO GETTING BACK HERE
FROM THE MORGUE, OXCART?

12:19.506 --> 12:23.608
I'VE BEEN TOLD THAT THE PICTURES
OF YOUR WIFE DID NOT GET POSTED

12:23.610 --> 12:26.444
ON SWEET REVENGE ONLINE
IN THE USUAL WAY.

12:26.446 --> 12:28.446
THAT'S RIGHT.
THEY WERE STOLEN.

12:28.448 --> 12:29.614
HOW DID THAT HAPPEN?

12:29.616 --> 12:31.382
I'VE BEEN AWAY
FROM MY FAMILY

12:31.384 --> 12:35.520
FOR THREE OF THE PAST FIVE
YEARS, AND KELLY -- MY WIFE --

12:35.522 --> 12:38.523
KELLY THOUGHT THE PICTURES
OF HERSELF

12:38.525 --> 12:41.559
MIGHT...BRIDGE
THE DISTANCE.

12:41.561 --> 12:45.864
PERSONAL PICTURES,
AND I KEPT THEM ON MY LAPTOP.

12:45.866 --> 12:47.732
SHE SENT YOU THESE PHOTOS
BY E-MAIL?

12:47.734 --> 12:49.934
TO MY PRIVATE ACCOUNT,
YES.

12:49.936 --> 12:54.806
AND THAT WOULD HAVE BEEN THE END
OF IT, EXCEPT COMING HOME,

12:54.808 --> 12:57.208
I HAD MY LAPTOP OUT
IN THE AIRPORT

12:57.210 --> 12:58.810
WHEN I GOT A PHONE CALL.

12:58.812 --> 13:00.411
I ANSWERED IT.

13:00.413 --> 13:03.281
I STOOD UP AND STRETCHED MY LEGS
FOR JUST ONE MINUTE,

13:03.283 --> 13:06.084
AND WHEN I SAT BACK DOWN,
MY LAPTOP WAS GONE.

13:06.086 --> 13:08.920
AND THAT'S HOW YOUR WIFE'S
PICTURES WERE POSTED

13:08.922 --> 13:11.389
ON THE SWEET REVENGE WEBSITE?

13:11.391 --> 13:13.258
YES.

13:13.260 --> 13:16.661
I TRIED
TO HAVE THEM TAKEN DOWN

13:16.663 --> 13:18.663
BEFORE ONE OF THE STUDENTS
IN HER 9th-GRADE MATH GLASS

13:18.665 --> 13:20.598
OR ANOTHER TEACHER
FOUND OUT,

13:20.600 --> 13:24.469
OR MY SON, WHO GOES
TO THE SAME SCHOOL, SAW THEM.

13:24.471 --> 13:26.171
[ SIGHS ]

13:26.173 --> 13:28.740
I WROTE MR. HALL AND
EXPLAINED THE SITUATION TO HIM

13:28.742 --> 13:29.908
AS BEST I COULD.

13:29.910 --> 13:31.442
HOW'D MR. HALL RESPOND?

13:31.444 --> 13:33.111
[ SIGHS ]

13:33.113 --> 13:36.581
[ Voice breaking ]
WITH LEWD PHOTOS OF HIMSELF

13:36.583 --> 13:39.851
SENT TO MY WIFE'S
E-MAIL ADDRESS,

13:39.853 --> 13:42.020
ASKING WHAT THE BIG DEAL
WITH NUDITY WAS.

13:42.022 --> 13:46.291
<i>SO I -- I PAID ONE OF THOSE</i>
<i>ONLINE-REPUTATION SERVICES</i>

13:46.293 --> 13:48.159
<i>TO MAKE THE PICTURES</i>
<i>OF KELLY DISAPPEAR,</i>

13:48.161 --> 13:50.261
<i>AND THEY WERE TAKEN DOWN</i>
<i>FOR LESS THAN A DAY.</i>

13:50.263 --> 13:53.464
[ SNIFFLES ]

13:53.466 --> 13:57.168
AND THEN SOMEONE
FROM HER SCHOOL SAW THEM.

13:57.170 --> 14:02.841
WORD GOT AROUND, AND MY SON...
HE SAW THE PICTURES.

14:03.876 --> 14:07.278
I TRIED TO EXPLAIN TO HIM
THAT THIS WAS MEANT TO BE

14:07.280 --> 14:09.948
SOMETHING PRIVATE
BETWEEN HIS MOM AND ME...

14:12.117 --> 14:15.220
BUT HE DIDN'T SEE IT
THAT WAY,

14:15.222 --> 14:16.955
AND NEITHER DID
THE PRINCIPAL,

14:16.957 --> 14:20.692
WHO GAVE KELLY THE CHOICE
BETWEEN RESIGNING [SNIFFLES]

14:20.694 --> 14:24.729
AND A HEARING IN FRONT
OF THE SCHOOL BOARD.

14:24.731 --> 14:29.400
SO, THAT DAY,
ON THE WAY HOME FROM SCHOOL,

14:29.402 --> 14:33.605
SHE PULLED THE CAR OVER,
ON THE SIDE OF THE ROAD, AND...

14:39.078 --> 14:42.113
SHE JUMPED FROM
THE COLORADO STREET BRIDGE.

14:45.351 --> 14:48.186
YES. YES, SHE DID.

14:48.188 --> 14:49.921
[ SNIFFLES ]

14:49.923 --> 14:54.158
I LOOKED AWAY FROM MY LAPTOP
FOR ONE MINUTE,

14:54.160 --> 14:56.427
AND THE WORLD CHANGED.

14:56.429 --> 14:59.030
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:59.032 --> 15:00.865
DO YOU HAVE ANY WEAPONS,
<i>LIEUTENANT PRICE?</i>

15:00.867 --> 15:02.600
AMY SAYS SCOTT WARD
COULD BE ON THE MOVE.

15:02.602 --> 15:04.335
WHERE THE HELL IS TAO?
DAMN IT!

15:04.337 --> 15:06.104
<i>I CAN GIVE YOU</i>
<i>THE COMBINATION</i>

15:06.106 --> 15:07.272
<i>AND CONSENT</i>
<i>TO SEARCH MY HOUSE.</i>

15:07.274 --> 15:10.708
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

15:10.710 --> 15:11.776
HELLO.

15:11.778 --> 15:13.511
TAO,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?!

15:13.513 --> 15:15.747
LOOKING AT WHAT IS LEFT
OF TRAVIS HALL'S HEAD.

15:15.749 --> 15:18.283
I WAS EXPECTING TO FIND
A WOUND

15:18.285 --> 15:20.018
CONSISTENT
WITH A 7.62 CARTRIDGE

15:20.020 --> 15:21.619
FIRED FROM
OVER 50 YARDS AWAY.

15:21.621 --> 15:24.122
BUT THE BULLET
ENTERED THE CRANIUM

15:24.124 --> 15:26.925
3 1/2 CENTIMETERS
RIGHT OF THE MIDLINE,

15:26.927 --> 15:30.128
AND THE WEAPON WAS PLACED
DIRECTLY AGAINST THE SCALP.

15:30.130 --> 15:34.966
THERE WAS DEFINITELY A SNIPER
SHOT FROM ACROSS THE STREET.

15:34.968 --> 15:37.068
RIGHT, AND I'M GLAD
I DON'T HAVE TO EXPLAIN THAT,

15:37.070 --> 15:38.870
BECAUSE THAT WAS NOT
THE CAUSE OF DEATH.

15:38.872 --> 15:42.040
THERE'S CIRCULAR STIPPLING
ON THE WOUND

15:42.042 --> 15:43.641
AND PATCHES OF BLOOD

15:43.643 --> 15:45.476
WHERE THE HAIR WAS YANKED
FROM YOUR VICTIM'S HEAD.

15:45.478 --> 15:50.815
YOU MEAN, UH, LIKE HE WAS...
LIKE THE KILLER...

15:50.817 --> 15:52.216
GRABBED THE VICTIM
FROM BEHIND.

15:52.218 --> 15:53.384
Right.

15:53.386 --> 15:55.053
DO NOT PULL MY HAIR.

15:55.055 --> 15:58.256
WITH HIS LEFT HAND,
WHILE WITH THE RIGHT,

15:58.258 --> 16:01.492
HE SHOT POINT-BLANK INTO
THE BACK OF HALL'S HEAD.

16:01.494 --> 16:04.662
SO, THE MURDER WEAPON
WAS POINTED...

16:04.664 --> 16:07.332
UP, YES, IT WAS.

16:17.076 --> 16:18.843
OOH.

16:20.946 --> 16:23.648
[ TELEPHONES RINGING ]

16:23.650 --> 16:24.983
OH, MY GOD.

16:24.985 --> 16:28.019
I'VE JUST BEEN PUTTING
ALL THIS PRESSURE

16:28.021 --> 16:31.956
ON A MAN WHO LOST HIS WIFE,
AND HE DIDN'T KILL HALL?

16:31.958 --> 16:35.526
NOT WITH A RIFLE, AND HERE'S
THE BULLET THAT DID THE JOB.

16:35.528 --> 16:38.096
IT'S FROM A 9mm HANDGUN.

16:38.098 --> 16:39.464
OKAY, SO, THE SAME NIGHT

16:39.466 --> 16:41.466
THAT TRAVIS HALL GETS
HIS HEAD BLOWN OFF,

16:41.468 --> 16:43.468
A SNIPER SETS UP
ACROSS THE STREET?

16:43.470 --> 16:45.136
THAT DOESN'T MAKE
ANY SENSE.

16:45.138 --> 16:47.372
UNLESS SOMEONE WAS TRYING
TO MISLEAD US.

16:47.374 --> 16:50.308
OUR KEY SUSPECT HAS
LONG-RANGE-WEAPONS TRAINING.

16:50.310 --> 16:53.344
KEITH PRICE,
ANGRY ARMY VET,

16:53.346 --> 16:55.713
SENDS A LETTER THREATENING
TO KILL TRAVIS HALL.

16:55.715 --> 16:58.182
COULD HAVE BEEN KNOWN
BY EVERYBODY

16:58.184 --> 17:01.886
WORKING AT SWEET REVENGE ONLINE,
INCLUDING SCOTT WARD.

17:07.559 --> 17:10.395
ALL RIGHT, SUBJECT
IS MOVING TOWARD OLIVE.

17:10.397 --> 17:12.463
THIS IS HIS THIRD TIME
AROUND THE BLOCK.

17:12.465 --> 17:15.233
I HAVE TO THINK HE'S WAITING
FOR SOMETHING...OR SOMEONE.

17:26.912 --> 17:29.313
HEY, WE GOT A BOGEY
AT THE JAGUAR.

17:33.419 --> 17:37.321
[ ARGUING INDISTINCTLY ]

17:37.323 --> 17:38.890
Scott: ME?
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU --

17:38.892 --> 17:40.591
YOU KNOW WHAT YOU DID.
W-- HEY!

17:44.696 --> 17:47.098
[ GUNFIRE ]

17:48.267 --> 17:50.201
Sykes: R-63, SHOTS FIRED
AT MY LOCATION

17:50.203 --> 17:51.602
FROM THE EAST SIDE
OF THE STREET.

17:51.604 --> 17:54.572
S.I.S. UNITS,
BLOCK OFF THE NORTH SIDE.

17:54.574 --> 17:56.607
LET'S GO.

17:56.609 --> 17:59.610
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

17:59.612 --> 18:00.945
SHOULD I ROLL PARAMEDICS?

18:00.947 --> 18:03.448
NO. THEY DON'T LOOK HURT.

18:06.285 --> 18:09.520
NUMBER ONE HAS
A SMALL-FRAME 9mm

18:09.522 --> 18:11.289
IN HIS POSSESSION.

18:11.291 --> 18:14.192
R-63, WE HAVE
A POSSIBLE SNIPER --

18:14.194 --> 18:15.626
LOCATION UNKNOWN.

18:15.628 --> 18:17.428
HAVE RESPONDING UNITS
SET UP A PERIMETER

18:17.430 --> 18:18.463
TO THE NORTH AND SOUTH.

18:18.465 --> 18:20.031
[ SIREN WAILS ]

18:20.033 --> 18:22.066
I REPEAT, WE HAVE A SNIPER.
APPROACH WITH CAUTION.

18:30.042 --> 18:32.710
Sykes:
SHOTS FIRED AT SCOTT WARD

18:32.712 --> 18:34.579
AND THE GUY HE WAS WITH
CAME FROM 7.62 CARTRIDGES.

18:34.581 --> 18:37.281
SAME AS THE RIFLE
AT OUR FIRST CRIME SCENE.

18:37.283 --> 18:40.218
ALSO THE SAME -- OUR SNIPER
DIDN'T HIT ANYBODY.

18:40.220 --> 18:42.220
BUT IN HIS COAT, SCOTT WARD
HAD A 9mm

18:42.222 --> 18:44.722
AND SINCE TRAVIS HALL WAS
SHOT WITH ONE OF THOSE,

18:44.724 --> 18:46.591
I SENT HIS WEAPON ON
TO BALLISTICS.

18:46.593 --> 18:49.393
WHATEVER YOU CAN GIVE US, CHIEF,
TO CATCH THIS SNIPER.

18:49.395 --> 18:51.963
I'VE GOT THE ENTIRE
NEIGHBORHOOD BLOCKED OFF,

18:51.965 --> 18:55.099
AND S.I.S. IS SEARCHING IT,
ALONG WITH 30 PATROL OFFICERS

18:55.101 --> 18:57.101
AND TWO DOGS TRAINED
IN FEAR SCENT.

18:57.103 --> 18:58.836
THE SNIPER
ISN'T GETTING AWAY,

18:58.838 --> 19:01.239
THOUGH HOW HE'S INVOLVED,
I DON'T KNOW.

19:01.241 --> 19:04.175
TELL US ABOUT THE MAN WHO GOT
INTO THE FIGHT WITH WARD.

19:04.177 --> 19:06.077
HIS I.D. SAYS
HE'S RYAN BROOKS,

19:06.079 --> 19:08.513
AND HIS NAME HAS A FLAG ON IT
FROM THE FBI.

19:08.515 --> 19:13.117
WELL, SINCE HE'S ABOUT
TO BECOME A DEPUTY CHIEF,

19:13.119 --> 19:15.520
MAYBE AGENT HOWARD WOULDN'T
MIND EXPLAINING THAT.

19:15.522 --> 19:18.156
I'LL HURRY WARDEN BROOKS
THROUGH BOOKING FOR YOU.

19:18.158 --> 19:20.758
MEANWHILE, I'M TAKING SYKES
BACK TO HELP COOPER.

19:20.760 --> 19:22.860
I FEEL THE NEED FOR A LITTLE
IN-PERSON SUPERVISION.

19:22.862 --> 19:24.195
MM-HMM.
KEEP ME POSTED.

19:24.197 --> 19:25.429
YES, SIR.

19:28.934 --> 19:31.335
[ DOOR OPENS ]

19:31.337 --> 19:33.871
SORRY WE'VE GONE SO LATE.

19:33.873 --> 19:37.308
LIEUTENANT MIKE IS BACK
AT THE SERVERS NOW,

19:37.310 --> 19:41.145
SO YOU AND RICKY ARE CLEARED
TO GO TO DINNER.

19:41.147 --> 19:42.446
HOW DOES THAT SOUND?

19:42.448 --> 19:44.048
OKAY.

19:44.050 --> 19:45.349
I'M SO SORRY.

19:45.351 --> 19:46.951
IF I WASN'T LOOKING
FOR A SNIPER,

19:46.953 --> 19:49.053
YOU KNOW --
I-I-IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT.

19:49.055 --> 19:53.457
BUT WE NEED TO RETHINK
THIS WHOLE ADOPTION THING,

19:53.459 --> 19:56.827
BECAUSE RICKY IS NOT
INTO IT AT ALL.

19:56.829 --> 19:59.564
A LITTLE PUSHBACK
FROM SIBLINGS IS NATURAL.

19:59.566 --> 20:01.699
WHEN I WAS PREGNANT
WITH RICKY,

20:01.701 --> 20:03.401
EMILY TOLD ME SEVERAL TIMES

20:03.403 --> 20:05.670
SHE DIDN'T WANT
A LITTLE BROTHER.

20:05.672 --> 20:08.005
SHE WAS 3.

20:08.007 --> 20:09.574
OH, THEY'RE ALWAYS 3.

20:09.576 --> 20:11.909
LOOK, RICKY HASN'T
THOUGHT THIS THROUGH.

20:11.911 --> 20:13.244
I CAN TELL.

20:13.246 --> 20:15.346
I'LL TALK TO HIM IN THE MORNING,
AND I'M SURE

20:15.348 --> 20:17.982
THAT WHATEVER ISSUE HE HAS,
WE CAN GET IT STRAIGHTENED OUT.

20:17.984 --> 20:20.251
SHARON, I KNOW YOU'RE
A GREAT DEAL MAKER AND --

20:20.253 --> 20:21.852
HEY.

20:21.854 --> 20:23.421
HEY.

20:23.423 --> 20:24.755
SERVERS ARE UP AND RUNNING.

20:24.757 --> 20:26.924
LIEUTENANT TAO CAN DO THE REST.

20:26.926 --> 20:29.427
SO, I'M READY WHENEVER
YOU ARE, RUSTY.

20:29.429 --> 20:30.828
HAVE YOU THOUGHT ABOUT

20:30.830 --> 20:34.899
WHERE YOU AND RUSTY
MIGHT LIKE TO GO EAT?

20:34.901 --> 20:36.334
OH, I'M -- I'M GONNA RAID
THE REFRIGERATOR

20:36.336 --> 20:37.368
WHEN I GET HOME.

20:37.370 --> 20:38.603
I'M -- I'M PRETTY TIRED.

20:38.605 --> 20:41.272
YEAH, IT'S ALMOST,
UH, WOW, 9:30.

20:41.274 --> 20:43.841
I'M SORRY YOU HAVE TO WORK LATE.
MM.

20:43.843 --> 20:45.610
OH.

20:45.612 --> 20:47.044
SEE YOU FOR BREAKFAST.

20:47.046 --> 20:49.614
I HOPE SO.
PROBABLY, YES.
GREAT.

20:49.616 --> 20:51.249
OKAY, WELL, IT LOOKS LIKE

20:51.251 --> 20:54.385
YOU HAVE YOUR WORK CUT OUT
FOR YOU, SO GOOD LUCK.

20:54.387 --> 20:56.621
THANK YOU, RUSTY.

20:56.623 --> 20:57.855
UM, YOU GUYS HAVE A GREAT NIGHT.

20:57.857 --> 20:59.957
MM-HMM.
LOVE YOU.

20:59.959 --> 21:02.627
LOVE YOU, TOO.

21:02.629 --> 21:04.295
Sanchez:
IT WASN'T A FIGHT, EXACTLY.

21:04.297 --> 21:05.563
RYAN BROOKS AND SCOTT WARD

21:05.565 --> 21:07.431
PUSHED EACH OTHER AROUND
IN PUBLIC --

21:07.433 --> 21:11.435
NOT VERY WELL, BUT WE CAN STILL
HOLD THEM ON BATTERY CHARGES.

21:11.437 --> 21:14.472
ANYTHING THE FBI CAN SHARE
WITH US ABOUT MR. BROOKS?

21:14.474 --> 21:16.607
HE INVESTS
IN HIGH-TECH STARTUPS.

21:16.609 --> 21:19.877
THE FBI INVESTIGATED HIM
FOR TAX EVASION -- GOT NOWHERE.

21:19.879 --> 21:22.079
WELL, MAYBE OUR OLD FRIEND
SCOTTY, HERE,

21:22.081 --> 21:23.447
WILL BE MORE FORTHCOMING

21:23.449 --> 21:25.483
NOW THAT SOMEBODY
IS SHOOTING AT HIM.

21:25.485 --> 21:28.052
PLUS, LIEUTENANT PRICE
WAS IN OUR CUSTODY

21:28.054 --> 21:29.620
WHEN THE SECOND SHOOTING
TOOK PLACE,

21:29.622 --> 21:31.155
SO HE COULDN'T HAVE BEEN
INVOLVED.

21:31.157 --> 21:33.491
I THINK WE SHOULD WAIT
UNTIL BALLISTICS IS FINISHED

21:33.493 --> 21:34.725
TESTING ALL THE WEAPONS
AT HIS HOUSE

21:34.727 --> 21:36.327
BEFORE RELEASING PRICE.

21:36.329 --> 21:39.930
SOMEONE WAS FRAMING
OUR ARMY RANGER FOR A REASON.

21:39.932 --> 21:42.233
MAYBE MR. WARD CAN TELL US WHY.

21:42.235 --> 21:44.435
Provenza:
JUST TO BE CLEAR, SCOTT,

21:44.437 --> 21:47.338
ARE YOU WAIVING YOUR RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY?

21:47.340 --> 21:48.739
OH, YEAH. YEAH.

21:48.741 --> 21:50.574
DO NOT CALL ALAN BURKE,
THAT BASTARD.

21:50.576 --> 21:53.110
HE'S THE ONE THAT TOLD RYAN
I WAS GETTING WEAK IN THE KNEES.

21:53.112 --> 21:54.645
YOU GUARANTEE MY SAFETY,

21:54.647 --> 21:57.281
AND I WILL TELL YOU
WHATEVER YOU WANT TO KNOW.

21:57.283 --> 22:00.685
OKAY. WELL, YOU REALIZE THAT
THE GUN THAT YOU'RE CONCEALING,

22:00.687 --> 22:05.856
THE RUGER LC9, IS THE EXACT
MAKE USED TO KILL TRAVIS?

22:05.858 --> 22:07.591
IF I KILLED TRAVIS
WITH THAT GUN,

22:07.593 --> 22:10.027
DO YOU REALLY THINK I'D BE
STUPID ENOUGH TO CARRY IT ON ME?

22:10.029 --> 22:12.463
YEAH, I NEEDED IT
TO DEFEND MYSELF.

22:12.465 --> 22:14.031
FROM RYAN BROOKS?

22:14.033 --> 22:16.033
W-WHY WOULD HE WANT
TO HURT YOU?

22:16.035 --> 22:19.370
'CAUSE THAT -- THAT IDIOT TRAVIS
WAS THREATENING HIM,

22:19.372 --> 22:20.871
DEMANDING MORE MONEY

22:20.873 --> 22:21.939
AND SAYING THAT IF HE DIDN'T GET
WHAT HE WANTED,

22:21.941 --> 22:23.307
HE WAS GONNA GO TO THE FBI.

22:23.309 --> 22:26.510
ABOUT THEIR LEGITIMATE
BUSINESS PRACTICES.

22:26.512 --> 22:28.713
RYAN ANSWERS TO POWERFUL PEOPLE,

22:28.715 --> 22:32.783
PEOPLE THAT WOULD BE VULNERABLE
TO QUESTIONABLE PUBLICITY.

22:32.785 --> 22:35.653
SO, THAT'S WHY YOU MET HIM
ON THE STREET,

22:35.655 --> 22:38.556
TO TALK ABOUT
A PUBLIC-RELATIONS PROBLEM?

22:38.558 --> 22:41.459
NO, NO, OBVIOUSLY, HE WANTED ME
TO GO OUT TO HIS CAR

22:41.461 --> 22:42.893
SO I WOULD BE IN THE OPEN.

22:42.895 --> 22:44.228
IT WAS A SETUP.

22:44.230 --> 22:45.896
RYAN TRIED TO HAVE ME
ASSASSINATED.

22:45.898 --> 22:47.832
HE'S PUSHING
THE SNIPER ANGLE.

22:47.834 --> 22:49.166
<i>OKAY.</i>
<i>SO DID WE.</i>

22:49.168 --> 22:52.169
EXCEPT THE SNIPER
HASN'T KILLED ANYONE.

22:52.171 --> 22:54.305
<i>YOU SAID WHY</i>
<i>HE WANTED TRAVIS DEAD.</i>

22:54.307 --> 22:55.873
<i>WHY DID HE WANT</i>
<i>TO KILL YOU?</i>

22:55.875 --> 22:59.510
BECAUSE I KNOW HOW OUR SITE TIES
TO HIS OTHER SITES,

22:59.512 --> 23:01.078
<i>WHICH IS WHERE</i>
<i>THE REAL MONEY IS.</i>

23:01.080 --> 23:02.480
THE REAL MONEY.

23:02.482 --> 23:05.783
W-WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"THE REAL MONEY"?

23:07.686 --> 23:08.786
I'LL TELL YOU.

23:10.822 --> 23:12.089
BUT FIRST, I NEED IMMUNITY.

23:12.091 --> 23:15.860
GET ME IMMUNITY.
I'LL TELL YOU EVERYTHING.

23:15.862 --> 23:19.497
THERE'S NOTHING TO TELL!
I'M NOT A KILLER!

23:19.499 --> 23:21.932
LOOK, I'M AN INVESTOR
WHO PROVIDES STARTUP CAPITAL

23:21.934 --> 23:23.667
FOR VARIOUS ONLINE ENTERPRISES.

23:23.669 --> 23:26.670
SIR, ARE YOU SAYING THAT --
THAT YOU HAD NOTHING TO DO

23:26.672 --> 23:29.740
WITH TRAVIS HALL'S DEATH,
NOTHING TO DO WITH THE SNIPER

23:29.742 --> 23:32.009
WHO SHOT AT SCOTT WARD
THIS AFTERNOON?

23:32.011 --> 23:33.677
SHOT AT SCOTT?!

23:33.679 --> 23:36.046
SCOTT LURED ME TO HIS APARTMENT
TO HAVE ME KILLED!

23:36.048 --> 23:37.615
YOU WANT TO GIVE IMMUNITY
TO SCOTT?!

23:37.617 --> 23:38.816
GIVE IT TO ME!

23:42.788 --> 23:44.722
I KNOW ALL OF THE SECRETS.

23:44.724 --> 23:47.458
I'M SURE WE CAN COME
TO AN UNDERSTANDING.

23:47.460 --> 23:50.127
WE'LL SEE ABOUT THAT.

23:50.129 --> 23:51.295
EXCUSE US.

23:57.035 --> 23:58.569
ALLOW ME TO PRESENT

23:58.571 --> 24:01.806
THE SERVER LOGS
FOR SWEET REVENGE ONLINE.

24:01.808 --> 24:04.642
OVER AND OVER, YOU CAN SEE

24:04.644 --> 24:07.077
THEY USED BUFFER OVERFLOW,
PATH NAME,

24:07.079 --> 24:08.646
AND SQL INJECTION ATTACKS

24:08.648 --> 24:11.315
TO EXPLOIT VULNERABILITIES
IN E-MAIL SERVERS.

24:11.317 --> 24:13.317
BUZZ.

24:13.319 --> 24:15.586
UH, SWEET REVENGE HACKED
INTO PEOPLE'S COMPUTERS

24:15.588 --> 24:16.720
TO STEAL IMAGES.

24:16.722 --> 24:19.390
AH. THANK YOU.
WE GOT IT.

24:19.392 --> 24:22.726
Fritz: THE L.A.P.D.
GOT FARTHER IN 12 HOURS

24:22.728 --> 24:24.562
THAN THE FBI DID
IN SIX MONTHS.

24:24.564 --> 24:27.097
YOU KNOW, I THINK
I'M GONNA LIKE IT OVER HERE.

24:27.099 --> 24:28.999
WELL, TO BE FAIR,
WE HAD A WARRANT.

24:29.001 --> 24:31.569
FEDERAL GOVERNMENT'S
COMPUTER FRAUD AND ABUSE ACT

24:31.571 --> 24:34.271
MAKES EVERY INSTANCE
OF UNAUTHORIZED ACCESS TO

24:34.273 --> 24:36.407
AND THEFT FROM PRIVATE
E-MAIL ACCOUNTS

24:36.409 --> 24:37.908
A CLASS "B" FELONY.

24:37.910 --> 24:40.010
IT'S PUNISHABLE BY UP
TO 20 YEARS IN PRISON.

24:40.012 --> 24:42.313
THERE'S HUNDREDS OF VIOLATIONS
IN THOSE RECORDS.

24:42.315 --> 24:44.515
AND THAT'S NOT JUST LEVERAGE.
THAT'S JUSTICE.

24:44.517 --> 24:46.684
AND SWEET REVENGE.
Sharon: WAIT.

24:46.686 --> 24:49.653
WAIT, WE STILL HAVE A SNIPER
OUT THERE,

24:49.655 --> 24:52.289
AND I DON'T KNOW HOW
HE CONNECTS.

24:52.291 --> 24:55.860
THIS IS WHY RYAN BROOKS WAS
TRYING TO KILL YOU, ISN'T IT?

24:55.862 --> 24:58.496
HE KNEW YOU COULD CUT A DEAL
ON THE HACKING CHARGES,

24:58.498 --> 25:01.365
LIKE TRAVIS TRIED TO DO,
AND SEND HIM TO PRISON FOR LIFE.

25:01.367 --> 25:03.801
N-NO. UM, THIS IS --
IT'S JUST PART OF THE CRIME.

25:03.803 --> 25:05.503
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
THE WHOLE THING?

25:05.505 --> 25:07.371
LET ME GET ANOTHER LAWYER --
NOT BURKE.

25:07.373 --> 25:09.273
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO. NO, NO.
NOW, YOU LISTEN TO ME.

25:09.275 --> 25:11.008
WE'VE GOT A SNIPER
ON THE LOOSE.

25:11.010 --> 25:13.043
WE CAN'T WAIT FOR YOU
TO GET A LAWYER.

25:13.045 --> 25:14.778
YOU WANT TO MAKE A DEAL?
FINE.

25:14.780 --> 25:17.014
WE'LL ARREST YOU,
TURN YOU OVER TO THE FBI.

25:17.016 --> 25:19.550
OR YOU CAN REVOKE YOUR RIGHT
TO COUNSEL,

25:19.552 --> 25:21.452
TELL US
THE WHOLE UGLY STORY.

25:21.454 --> 25:24.688
WE CAN WORK ON LENIENCY LATER,
BASED ON YOUR COOPERATION.

25:24.690 --> 25:28.459
BUT IF WHILE WE'RE STANDING HERE
THE SNIPER KILLS SOMEONE,

25:28.461 --> 25:30.060
YOU'RE ON YOUR OWN.

25:30.062 --> 25:33.664
SO, YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT AND BE AN IDIOT

25:33.666 --> 25:35.866
AND TO GET A LAWYER
AND GO TO JAIL

25:35.868 --> 25:37.501
FOR THE REST OF YOUR LIFE.

25:37.503 --> 25:43.073
OR...YOU COULD REVOKE
AND HELP US.

25:43.075 --> 25:44.942
IT'S UP TO YOU.

25:52.851 --> 25:54.184
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

25:54.186 --> 25:56.320
NO, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT!

25:56.322 --> 25:57.821
<i>HOLD ON, HOLD ON.</i>

25:57.823 --> 25:59.156
<i>I REVOKE.</i>

25:59.158 --> 26:01.325
<i>ALL RIGHT?</i>

26:01.327 --> 26:03.060
[ PANTING ]
NOW, HERE'S THE DEAL.

26:03.062 --> 26:05.329
WHEN RYAN AND I STARTED
SWEET REVENGE ONLINE,

26:05.331 --> 26:07.598
<i>WE HAD NO IDEA HOW MUCH MONEY</i>
<i>WE COULD MAKE,</i>

26:07.600 --> 26:10.000
<i>BUT RYAN KNEW NO MATTER</i>
<i>WHAT OUR SITE TOOK IN,</i>

26:10.002 --> 26:12.503
<i>HE WOULD MAKE 10 TIMES</i>
<i>AS MUCH LINKING OFF OF IT.</i>

26:12.505 --> 26:13.771
WHAT KIND OF LINKS?

26:13.773 --> 26:15.606
ALL THOSE REPUTATION SERVICES

26:15.608 --> 26:18.075
PROMISING
TO SCRUB PEOPLE'S PICTURES

26:18.077 --> 26:21.512
OFF OF SWEET REVENGE ONLINE
IN EXCHANGE FOR CASH.

26:21.514 --> 26:23.113
THOSE WERE RYAN'S.

26:24.749 --> 26:28.385
SO, HE WAS USING
YOUR WEBSITE

26:28.387 --> 26:30.688
AS A STARTING POINT
FOR BLACKMAIL.

26:30.690 --> 26:32.523
PEOPLE PAY.

26:32.525 --> 26:34.358
HE JUST PUTS THE PICTURES
SOMEWHERE ELSE.

26:34.360 --> 26:35.693
THEY PAY AGAIN.

26:35.695 --> 26:37.394
THEY POP UP AGAIN,
OVER AND OVER.

26:37.396 --> 26:39.597
EVENTUALLY, PEOPLE --
YOU KNOW, THEY JUST --

26:39.599 --> 26:41.632
THEY RUN OUT OF MONEY,
OR THEY...GIVE UP.

26:41.634 --> 26:43.200
OR COMMIT SUICIDE.

26:43.202 --> 26:46.637
[ SIGHS ]

26:46.639 --> 26:48.872
HACKING JUST GOT ELEVATED
TO EXTORTION.

26:48.874 --> 26:51.141
IF TRAVIS WAS THREATENING
TO EXPOSE THEM,

26:51.143 --> 26:52.710
THAT'S MOTIVE FOR HIS MURDER.

26:52.712 --> 26:54.311
BUT WHO PULLED THE TRIGGER?

26:54.313 --> 26:56.280
HMM.

26:56.282 --> 26:58.382
[ DOG BARKING ]

27:16.434 --> 27:18.836
COME UP SLOWLY
WITH YOUR HANDS RAISED.

27:18.838 --> 27:20.104
SLOWLY SO WE CAN SEE THEM.
NOW!

27:20.106 --> 27:21.672
Connor:
OKAY, OKAY, OKAY.

27:21.674 --> 27:24.341
OKAY, I'M SITTING UP, SO
DON'T -- DON'T SHOOT ME, PLEASE.

27:24.343 --> 27:25.676
[ BARKING CONTINUES ]

27:43.094 --> 27:44.762
[ KEYS CLACKING ]

27:44.764 --> 27:46.830
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

27:46.832 --> 27:47.865
MORNING, MOM.

27:47.867 --> 27:48.999
MORNING, DARLING.

27:49.001 --> 27:50.200
FIND YOUR SHOOTER?

27:50.202 --> 27:52.469
OUR SNIPER, YES.

27:52.471 --> 27:55.706
AS IT TURNS OUT, HE WAS
THE SON OF AN ARMY RANGER.

27:55.708 --> 27:57.274
HIS MOTHER
COMMITTED SUICIDE.

27:57.276 --> 27:59.276
HE'S A VERY TROUBLED
YOUNG MAN.
HMM.

27:59.278 --> 28:01.545
YOU'RE NOT GONNA BE
ADOPTING HIM, TOO, ARE YOU?

28:04.449 --> 28:07.184
LET'S DISCUSS THIS ADOPTION,

28:07.186 --> 28:10.688
BECAUSE I FEEL
YOUR LACK OF ENTHUSIASM

28:10.690 --> 28:12.690
FROM A GREAT DISTANCE,

28:12.692 --> 28:17.728
AND I'D LIKE TO KNOW...
WHAT'S THAT ABOUT?

28:19.364 --> 28:21.832
OKAY.

28:21.834 --> 28:25.636
[ SIGHS ]
RIGHT OFF THE BAT,

28:25.638 --> 28:27.171
I WANT YOU TO KNOW

28:27.173 --> 28:29.206
THAT I UNDERSTAND A LOT
OF WHAT YOU'RE GOING THROUGH.

28:29.208 --> 28:30.641
DAD WAS A LETDOWN
AS A HUSBAND.

28:30.643 --> 28:32.910
EMILY LEFT FOR NEW YORK
TO DO HER BALLET THING.

28:32.912 --> 28:34.211
I LEFT FOR PALO ALTO.

28:34.213 --> 28:35.846
I DON'T MAKE IT HOME
ALL THAT OFTEN.

28:35.848 --> 28:37.581
YOU WORK ALL THE TIME.

28:37.583 --> 28:40.084
IT'S A RECIPE
FOR LONELINESS.

28:40.086 --> 28:41.485
AND -- AND I -- MOM,

28:41.487 --> 28:43.654
I HAVE A LOT OF SYMPATHY
FOR YOU ON THAT SCORE.

28:43.656 --> 28:46.857
AND, ALSO, YOU ARE
INCREDIBLY GIVING AND CARING,

28:46.859 --> 28:49.393
BUT, MOM, T-T-THAT KID,
HE IS -- HE'S A HUSTLER,

28:49.395 --> 28:51.995
AND HE'S --
AND A CON ARTIST,

28:51.997 --> 28:53.831
AND I THINK THAT
HE'S TAKEN ADVANTAGE OF YOU.

28:53.833 --> 28:57.101
A-AND LOOK -- LOOK,
YOU DID SO MUCH FOR ME.

28:57.103 --> 28:59.870
YOU WERE TOUGH AND HONEST
WHEN I NEEDED IT,

28:59.872 --> 29:01.939
AND NOW I THINK I NEED
TO DO THE SAME FOR YOU.

29:01.941 --> 29:05.743
I NEED TO TAKE THE HIT
LIKE YOU DID

29:05.745 --> 29:08.445
AND -- AND BE THE BAD GUY
FOR A MINUTE AND STEP IN

29:08.447 --> 29:10.514
TO SAY THAT THIS IS
NOT A GOOD IDEA.

29:10.516 --> 29:13.851
[ SIGHS ]

29:13.853 --> 29:16.453
MAY I ASK, HAVE YOU,
BY ANY CHANCE,

29:16.455 --> 29:19.456
BEEN TALKING WITH YOUR FATHER
ABOUT THIS?

29:19.458 --> 29:20.891
YEAH,
WE TALKED A FEW TIMES.

29:20.893 --> 29:22.226
I MEAN, HE'S --
HE'S WORRIED ABOUT YOU.

29:22.228 --> 29:24.061
MOM, I'M WORRIED ABOUT YOU.
I AM.

29:24.063 --> 29:26.296
LIKE, HELPING THE KID
A LITTLE BIT,

29:26.298 --> 29:29.566
THAT'S GREAT, BUT T-T-T-TO MAKE
HIM LEGALLY YOUR SON --

29:29.568 --> 29:30.901
I JUST -- I THINK

29:30.903 --> 29:33.871
THAT WE NEED TO TAKE
A GIANT STEP BACK, HERE,

29:33.873 --> 29:36.106
AND JUST RE-EVAL--
HOLD ON. HOLD ON.

29:36.108 --> 29:37.875
BEFORE WE GO BACK,

29:37.877 --> 29:41.712
I SHOULD CLEAR UP A BIG
MISUNDERSTANDING THAT YOU HAVE.

29:41.714 --> 29:43.247
OKAY.

29:43.249 --> 29:46.316
I'M NOT ASKING YOUR PERMISSION
TO ADOPT RUSTY,

29:46.318 --> 29:48.986
OR EMILY'S PERMISSION.

29:48.988 --> 29:50.654
I SEE GREAT THINGS
IN THIS BOY,

29:50.656 --> 29:52.289
AND I MEAN THAT
FROM THE BOTTOM

29:52.291 --> 29:54.558
OF MY EVER-SO-LONELY
HEART.
COME ON, MOM.

29:54.560 --> 29:57.161
YOU KNOW THAT I DID NOT MEAN
LONELINESS AS A CRITICISM.

29:57.163 --> 29:58.962
I WAS ONLY POINTING OUT
THE FACT --

29:58.964 --> 30:00.898
IT'S CLEAR
WHAT YOU'RE POINTING OUT.

30:00.900 --> 30:02.499
NOW I'M POINTING OUT
TO YOU --

30:02.501 --> 30:04.434
IF YOU DON'T DEVELOP
A LITTLE HUMAN COMPASSION

30:04.436 --> 30:05.836
FOR THIS YOUNG MAN

30:05.838 --> 30:08.939
WHO GREW UP WITH
NONE OF THE ADVANTAGES

30:08.941 --> 30:12.342
YOU TOOK FOR GRANTED
EVERY DAY OF YOUR LIFE,

30:12.344 --> 30:13.944
THEN I'M GONNA LEAVE HERE

30:13.946 --> 30:17.114
WONDERING WHERE I WENT WRONG
AS A MOTHER.
MOM.

30:17.116 --> 30:18.949
MOM, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT,
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT.

30:18.951 --> 30:20.450
HANG ON.

30:20.452 --> 30:23.854
LOOK, I-I'M -- I'M GONNA
HAVE CHILDREN ONE DAY.

30:23.856 --> 30:25.122
SO IS EMILY.

30:25.124 --> 30:26.323
DO YOU REALLY WANT
YOUR GRANDKIDS

30:26.325 --> 30:27.958
CALLING THAT BOY
"UNCLE RUSTY"?

30:27.960 --> 30:29.526
THAT IS A WHOLE LOT BETTER

30:29.528 --> 30:31.295
THAN WHAT I'M THINKING
OF CALLING YOU RIGHT NOW.

30:31.297 --> 30:32.796
MOM!

30:32.798 --> 30:35.365
RICHARD WILLIAM RAYDOR,
YOU LISTEN TO ME,

30:35.367 --> 30:36.967
AND YOU LISTEN TO ME GOOD.

30:36.969 --> 30:39.369
YOU'VE GOT ONE CHANCE
TO GET THIS RIGHT.

30:39.371 --> 30:42.639
YOU NEED TO TURN YOUR ATTITUDE
AROUND RIGHT THIS MINUTE,

30:42.641 --> 30:45.809
BECAUSE IF YOU MAKE RUSTY
FEEL UNWELCOME IN THIS FAMILY

30:45.811 --> 30:47.945
AFTER ALL OF HIS
AND MY HARD WORK,

30:47.947 --> 30:52.115
I WILL BE JUST
SO...DISAPPOINTED.

30:52.117 --> 30:54.318
OH, MY GOD.

30:54.320 --> 30:56.854
I AM SO DISAPPOINTED IN YOU
RIGHT NOW,

30:56.856 --> 30:59.056
I DON'T EVEN KNOW
WHAT TO SAY.

31:09.234 --> 31:12.836
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

31:12.838 --> 31:16.006
Sykes: THE ATTACKS LOOK LIKE
A FATHER-SON ASSASSINATION TEAM.

31:16.008 --> 31:17.507
GIVEN HIS AGE

31:17.509 --> 31:19.509
AND THE CIRCUMSTANCES
OF HIS MOTHER'S DEATH,

31:19.511 --> 31:21.745
IT'S A LITTLE EASIER
TO UNDERSTAND.

31:21.747 --> 31:23.647
Tao:
AND THOUGH THE OTHER GUNS

31:23.649 --> 31:25.515
FROM LIEUTENANT PRICE'S HOUSE
DIDN'T MATCH UP TO THE MURDER,

31:25.517 --> 31:28.252
THE SNIPER RIFLE WE FOUND
WITH CONNOR --

31:28.254 --> 31:29.720
IT WAS USED IN BOTH ATTACKS.

31:29.722 --> 31:31.755
THE BOY HAS BEEN READ
HIS RIGHTS, AND HE'LL TALK,

31:31.757 --> 31:33.891
BUT MAYBE WE SHOULDN'T
ASK HIM IF HE --

31:33.893 --> 31:36.326
NO, WE HAVE TO DO THIS IN ORDER.

31:36.328 --> 31:38.428
Flynn: WE ALREADY KNOW
WHAT HE'S GONNA SAY,

31:38.430 --> 31:40.497
AND TWO CONFESSIONS
COULD GUM UP THE WORKS.

31:40.499 --> 31:42.532
BUT THEY COULD ALSO BE
A SOLUTION.

31:42.534 --> 31:45.102
JUST BE READY TO FOLLOW UP
WITH THE FATHER.

31:45.104 --> 31:46.770
AMY, LET'S HEAR THE BOY OUT.

31:46.772 --> 31:49.106
Connor:
I KILLED TRAVIS HALL.

31:49.108 --> 31:53.110
SAME WAY I TRIED TO KILL
SCOTT WARD, BUT I MISSED.

31:53.112 --> 31:55.946
AND I -- I DID IT
ON MY OWN,

31:55.948 --> 31:58.949
SO MY FATHER KNOWS NOTHING
ABOUT IT.

31:58.951 --> 32:00.684
SO, HOW'D YOU KILL TRAVIS?

32:02.553 --> 32:05.022
I JUST -- I SET UP ON THE
BUILDING ACROSS THE STREET,

32:05.024 --> 32:06.957
AND WHEN I SAW HIM
IN THE WINDOW, I SHOT.

32:06.959 --> 32:08.025
IT WAS EASY.

32:08.027 --> 32:09.493
WHAT TIME WAS THAT?

32:12.196 --> 32:13.563
I -- I DON'T KNOW.

32:13.565 --> 32:16.300
SOMETIMES BETWEEN 11:30
AND 12:00.

32:16.302 --> 32:19.803
SO, YOU FIRED
THROUGH THE WINDOW,

32:19.805 --> 32:22.472
AND YOU SHOT TRAVIS
FROM ACROSS THE STREET?

32:22.474 --> 32:25.309
YEAH.
WRONG ANSWER.

32:25.311 --> 32:28.378
TRAVIS HALL WASN'T KILLED
BY A PSG1

32:28.380 --> 32:30.480
BUT BY A HANDGUN,
UP CLOSE.

32:30.482 --> 32:33.750
YOU DIDN'T HAVE ANYTHING TO DO
WITH HIS MURDER, DID YOU?

32:33.752 --> 32:35.118
YEAH, I DID.

32:35.120 --> 32:36.620
YEAH, NO, I KILLED HIM
FROM ACROSS THE STREET.

32:36.622 --> 32:39.823
MAYBE YOU THOUGHT THAT
YOU WERE HELPING YOUR DAD

32:39.825 --> 32:41.491
BY SHOOTING AT THIS MAN,

32:41.493 --> 32:44.995
BUT YOU'RE NOT HELPING HIM
OR YOURSELF NOW BY LYING.

32:44.997 --> 32:46.797
I'M NOT LYING, ALL RIGHT?

32:46.799 --> 32:47.998
NO, I KILLED TRAVIS.

32:48.000 --> 32:49.733
I KILLED HIM
BECAUSE HE KILLED MY MOM.

32:49.735 --> 32:50.968
YOUR MOTHER COMMITTED SUICIDE.

32:50.970 --> 32:53.103
NO, HE MADE HER DO THAT,
ALL RIGHT?!

32:53.105 --> 32:55.605
SHE -- SHE WAS FINE
BEFORE, OKAY?

32:55.607 --> 32:57.307
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

32:57.309 --> 33:01.011
AND MY MOTHER...I NEVER GOT
THE CHANCE TO TELL HER...

33:02.513 --> 33:04.648
[ SNIFFLES ]
[ Voice breaking ] I SAID

33:04.650 --> 33:06.650
SOME REALLY TERRIBLE THINGS
TO HER.

33:06.652 --> 33:08.185
LISTEN TO ME, CONNOR.

33:08.187 --> 33:10.620
I'M A MOTHER,
AND I PROMISE YOU,

33:10.622 --> 33:12.823
YOUR MOTHER KNEW YOU WERE SORRY.

33:12.825 --> 33:14.358
NO, SHE DIDN'T.

33:14.360 --> 33:15.759
[ SNIFFLES ]
SHE DIDN'T KNOW.

33:15.761 --> 33:17.427
IF SHE KNEW,
SHE WOULDN'T HAVE JUMPED.

33:17.429 --> 33:19.329
SHE DID KNOW.

33:19.331 --> 33:23.000
MOTHERS KNOW, AND WHATEVER YOU
SAID, NO MATTER HOW TERRIBLE,

33:23.002 --> 33:26.703
THAT IS NOT WHY YOUR MOTHER
KILLED HERSELF.

33:26.705 --> 33:29.039
AND YOU'RE NOT MAKING THINGS
BETTER FOR HER

33:29.041 --> 33:30.874
BY SAYING YOU KILLED PEOPLE
WHEN YOU DIDN'T,

33:30.876 --> 33:32.976
SO TELL US THE TRUTH.

33:32.978 --> 33:35.879
WHY DID YOU FIRE YOUR GUN
AT THOSE MEN YESTERDAY?

33:35.881 --> 33:37.881
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

33:39.717 --> 33:44.721
LOOK [SNIFFLES]
I DID KILL TRAVIS, OKAY?

33:44.723 --> 33:46.223
I KILLED HIM.

33:46.225 --> 33:48.892
NOW, WHATEVER I SAID BEFORE,
I -- I WAS -- I MEAN,

33:48.894 --> 33:51.895
I WAS JUST LYING ABOUT HOW,
BUT -- BUT I KILLED HIM, OKAY?

33:51.897 --> 33:54.231
SO, YOU CAN LET
MY DAD GO NOW, OKAY?

33:54.233 --> 33:55.999
I MEAN, YOU HAVE ME NOW,

33:56.001 --> 34:00.470
<i>SO -- SO PLEASE,</i>
<i>JUST LET HIM GO.</i>

34:00.472 --> 34:01.972
<i>PLEASE.</i>

34:01.974 --> 34:04.408
<i>HOW MUCH LONGER</i>
<i>AM I GONNA BE HELD HERE</i>

34:04.410 --> 34:06.176
<i>WITHOUT BEING CHARGED?</i>

34:06.178 --> 34:08.745
<i>WELL, WE'LL BE RELEASING YOU</i>
<i>SOON, MR. PRICE.</i>

34:08.747 --> 34:12.716
<i>WE HAVE A CONFESSION</i>
<i>IN THE MURDER OF TRAVIS HALL,</i>

34:12.718 --> 34:14.184
AND WE APPREHENDED THE SNIPER

34:14.186 --> 34:17.387
WHO ALSO FIRED UPON
TWO OTHER MEN

34:17.389 --> 34:19.189
WHILE YOU WERE IN CUSTODY
YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.

34:19.191 --> 34:22.859
SAME RIFLE WAS USED IN BOTH
SHOOTINGS, SO THAT'S IT.

34:22.861 --> 34:26.930
IF YOU DON'T MIND MY ASKING,
WHO KILLED HALL?

34:26.932 --> 34:31.835
OH, WELL, WE'RE SORRY TO HAVE
TO TELL YOU THIS, SIR,

34:31.837 --> 34:33.437
BUT IT WAS YOUR SON, CONNOR.

34:35.873 --> 34:38.108
THAT'S NOT --
THAT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

34:38.110 --> 34:39.409
HE ALREADY CONFESSED.

34:39.411 --> 34:41.545
BUT THE GOOD NEWS IS
SINCE HE'S 15,

34:41.547 --> 34:43.747
HE CAN'T BE SENTENCED
AS AN ADULT.

34:43.749 --> 34:46.283
NO, NO, NO, NO, NO.
HOLD ON. HOLD ON.

34:46.285 --> 34:50.053
WAIT.
CONNOR'S INNOCENT.

34:50.055 --> 34:51.788
[ <i>BREATHING HEAVILY</i> ]

34:51.790 --> 34:54.891
<i>IF YOU LOOK CLOSELY</i>
<i>AT THE PHYSICAL EVIDENCE,</i>

34:54.893 --> 34:58.462
<i>YOU'LL SEE THAT HALL</i>
<i>WASN'T KILLED BY A SNIPER.</i>

34:58.464 --> 35:00.997
HE WAS SHOT CLOSE-RANGE
WITH A 9mm HANDGUN.

35:02.033 --> 35:04.901
REALLY?
HOW DO YOU KNOW THAT?

35:04.903 --> 35:06.970
BECAUSE AFTER MY WIFE DIED,

35:06.972 --> 35:10.307
I COULDN'T GET TRAVIS' FACE
OUT OF MY MIND,

35:10.309 --> 35:11.975
SO I BLEW IT OFF HIS HEAD!

35:11.977 --> 35:13.577
<i>THAT'S HOW I KNOW.</i>

35:13.579 --> 35:15.245
HOW IS THIS ANYTHING

35:15.247 --> 35:18.381
EXCEPT PREMEDITATED MURDER
IN THE FIRST?

35:18.383 --> 35:19.416
I DON'T KNOW.

35:19.418 --> 35:20.750
WE NEED TO REMIND YOU,

35:20.752 --> 35:22.152
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

35:22.154 --> 35:23.553
I'VE ALREADY WAIVED!
OKAY.

35:25.156 --> 35:27.791
LET'S START...WITH HOW

35:27.793 --> 35:29.993
YOU GAINED ENTRY
INTO HALL'S APARTMENT.

35:29.995 --> 35:31.728
IT WAS EASY.

35:31.730 --> 35:33.730
I PAID ONE OF HALL'S WHORES
TO GET THE SECURITY CODE.

35:33.732 --> 35:37.434
ANY PARTICULAR REASON
WHY YOU CHOSE A 9mm RUGER?

35:37.436 --> 35:39.069
I SET UP A COMPUTER ALERT

35:39.071 --> 35:41.938
FOR ANYTHING TO DO
WITH SWEET REVENGE ONLINE,

35:41.940 --> 35:45.842
WHICH POINTED ME TO AN INSTAGRAM
PHOTO OF SCOTT WARD

35:45.844 --> 35:47.611
WAVING HIS RUGER AROUND
AT A PARTY.

35:47.613 --> 35:49.779
OKAY, W-- LET ME GET
THIS STRAIGHT.

35:49.781 --> 35:52.349
Y-YOU WANTED TO FRAME
SCOTT WARD, BUT FIRST,

35:52.351 --> 35:54.084
YOU WANTED TO FRAME YOURSELF
WITH A SNIPER SHOT?

35:54.086 --> 35:55.585
WHY?

35:55.587 --> 35:58.588
SO YOU'D LOOK AT ME HARD
OFF THE BAT, AND THEN,

35:58.590 --> 36:00.824
WHEN YOU FOUND
THE SECOND BULLET,

36:00.826 --> 36:03.193
YOU'D GO AFTER WARD
OR RYAN BROOKS.

36:03.195 --> 36:06.663
I GUESS I JUST OVERESTIMATED
YOUR SKILL AS INVESTIGATORS.

36:06.665 --> 36:09.699
WAIT, YOU HAD YOUR SON FIRE
UPON THESE OTHER TWO MEN

36:09.701 --> 36:12.169
WHILE YOU WERE IN CUSTODY

36:12.171 --> 36:14.504
BECAUSE YOU THOUGHT
YOU FRAMED YOURSELF TOO WELL?!

36:14.506 --> 36:16.339
NO, NO. THAT --
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

36:16.341 --> 36:18.942
THAT WAS NEVER THE PLAN.

36:18.944 --> 36:20.877
HE DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT I WAS DOING.

36:20.879 --> 36:24.548
YOUR SON DID FIRE AT BROOKS
AND WARD YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.

36:24.550 --> 36:26.216
IT'S ONLY LUCK
THAT NO ONE WAS WOUNDED.

36:26.218 --> 36:28.852
IT'S NOT LUCK!

36:28.854 --> 36:31.154
I TAUGHT CONNOR TO SHOOT,

36:31.156 --> 36:36.393
SO IF HE DIDN'T HIT ANYBODY,
HE WAS TRYING TO MISS.

36:42.466 --> 36:43.633
WRITE IT ALL DOWN.

36:43.635 --> 36:46.870
[ SIGHS ]

36:46.872 --> 36:51.408
I LOOKED AWAY FROM MY LAPTOP
FOR ONE MINUTE.

36:51.410 --> 36:54.578
YEAH? WELL, YOU LOOKED AWAY
FROM YOUR SON, TOO.

36:56.514 --> 36:58.481
IT'S GETTING TO BE A BAD HABIT
FOR YOU.

37:01.552 --> 37:05.322
WRITE IT ALL DOWN,
AND WE'LL SEE HOW IT CHECKS OUT.

37:05.324 --> 37:09.092
THEN MAYBE
WE CAN HELP YOUR SON.

37:16.434 --> 37:18.368
WHAT WILL HAPPEN TO THE BOY?

37:18.370 --> 37:22.939
CAN'T JUST WALK AWAY.
HE ENDANGERED LIVES.

37:22.941 --> 37:25.108
WELL, HE SHOULDN'T SPEND THE
NEXT 10 YEARS IN PRISON, EITHER,

37:25.110 --> 37:27.544
JUST FOR TRYING
TO PROTECT A PARENT.

37:27.546 --> 37:29.212
HIS IMPULSE WAS RIGHT.

37:29.214 --> 37:32.382
IT'S THE WAY HE ACTED ON IT
THAT REQUIRES A RESPONSE.

37:32.384 --> 37:35.919
BAD IMPULSE CONTROL.

37:35.921 --> 37:38.622
THAT'S WHAT KEEPS US ALL
IN BUSINESS.

37:40.858 --> 37:45.629
WELCOME TO THE L.A.P.D.,
SOON-TO-BE DEPUTY CHIEF HOWARD.

37:45.631 --> 37:48.465
WELCOME TO THE L.A.P.D.

37:53.871 --> 37:57.140
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

38:02.246 --> 38:03.947
UH, YOU KNOW, MOM, SOMEDAY SOON,

38:03.949 --> 38:06.783
YOU AND RUSTY ARE GONNA HAVE TO
COME TO SAN FRANCISCO

38:06.785 --> 38:08.752
AND LET ME TAKE YOU
TO THIS PLACE.

38:08.754 --> 38:10.654
GOT THE BEST DUMPLINGS
IN THE WORLD.

38:10.656 --> 38:11.788
HUH.

38:11.790 --> 38:13.423
WELL, FROM ALL THE STUFF

38:13.425 --> 38:16.092
YOU'VE BEEN INVITING US
TO DO TONIGHT,

38:16.094 --> 38:18.495
IT SOUNDS LIKE
EVERYTHING'S BETTER UP NORTH.

38:18.497 --> 38:21.598
HOW DID YOU MANAGE TO SURVIVE
GROWING UP HERE IN L.A.?

38:21.600 --> 38:23.600
WELL, IT'S NOT SO BAD
BEING HERE --

38:23.602 --> 38:25.835
YOU KNOW, IF YOU DON'T MIND
BREATHING AIR YOU CAN SEE.

38:25.837 --> 38:27.170
AND HOW WOULD YOU DESCRIBE

38:27.172 --> 38:29.172
INHALING ALL OF THE FOG
WHERE YOU LIVE?

38:29.174 --> 38:30.840
[ LAUGHS ]

38:30.842 --> 38:33.843
FUNNY. HE'S A FUNNY GUY.

38:34.845 --> 38:37.681
OKAY.

38:37.683 --> 38:39.616
FUNNY GUY.

38:39.618 --> 38:42.752
I HAVE ONE QUESTION
FOR YOU...

38:42.754 --> 38:44.321
BEFORE YOU
OFFICIALLY BECOME

38:44.323 --> 38:46.256
THE LITTLE BROTHER
I NEVER WANTED.

38:49.160 --> 38:51.594
I'M INTERESTED IN WHAT
YOUR IDEA OF FAMILY IS

38:51.596 --> 38:56.299
AND WHAT THE WORD MEANS
TO YOU -- "FAMILY."

38:56.301 --> 39:04.441
WELL...I GUESS...IT MEANS
THAT THE PEOPLE IN YOUR LIFE

39:04.443 --> 39:10.380
WHO YOU'VE DECIDED T-- TO LOVE
NO MATTER WHAT,

39:10.382 --> 39:17.220
AND THE PEOPLE WHO
ARE GOING TO LOVE YOU BACK

39:17.222 --> 39:19.556
NO MATTER WHAT.

39:22.727 --> 39:25.228
Sharon:
SOUNDS PRETTY GOOD TO ME --

39:25.230 --> 39:27.230
LOVING EACH OTHER
NO MATTER WHAT.

39:27.232 --> 39:30.433
NOT BAD.

39:32.503 --> 39:35.505
ALL RIGHT, LITTLE BROTHER.

39:35.507 --> 39:38.675
ANY QUESTIONS FOR ME?

39:38.677 --> 39:43.413
YEAH.
UH, JUST ONE.

39:43.415 --> 39:44.748
SHOOT.

39:46.183 --> 39:47.917
WHO CUTS YOUR HAIR?

39:47.919 --> 39:50.420
[ LAUGHS ]
W-WHAT?

39:50.422 --> 39:52.522
[ SNORTS ]

39:52.524 --> 39:53.690
DON'T SNORT-LAUGH.
I --

39:53.692 --> 39:55.759
[ LAUGHS ]
DON'T BE LAUGHING.

39:57.094 --> 39:58.695
I CUT MY HAIR.

39:58.697 --> 40:00.997
[ Laughing ] IT SAVES ME TONS
OF MONEY. WHAT?

40:00.999 --> 40:03.666
[ Laughing ]
WELL, THAT EXPLAINS IT.

40:03.668 --> 40:05.201
OH, OH.

40:05.203 --> 40:07.704
OKAY, ARE --
Y-- ALL RIGHT.

40:07.706 --> 40:11.007
LIKE A LOT OF OTHER DECISIONS
I'VE MADE RECENTLY,

40:11.009 --> 40:13.676
I AM...RETHINKING IT.

40:13.678 --> 40:15.211
THANK GOD.
[ LAUGHS ]

40:15.213 --> 40:17.947
I AM.
I'M RETHINK-- STOP IT.

40:17.949 --> 40:19.416
I'M RETHINKING IT.

40:19.418 --> 40:22.018
Fritz: HAVE YOU HEARD BACK
FROM THE D.A.

40:22.020 --> 40:24.020
ABOUT THAT BOY,
CONNOR PRICE?

40:24.022 --> 40:26.956
SUPERVISED PROBATION AND
THERAPY, LIVING WITH HIS AUNT.

40:26.958 --> 40:28.625
IT'S THE BEST WE COULD DO.

40:28.627 --> 40:30.627
[ SIGHS ]
I GUESS IT IS.

40:30.629 --> 40:33.830
LAST ONE.

40:34.799 --> 40:36.533
AND THANKS FOR YOUR HELP.

40:36.535 --> 40:40.036
MAYBE AN EX-FBI GUY CAN WORK
OUT OVER HERE AFTER ALL.

40:40.038 --> 40:42.472
THANKS FOR THE VOTE
OF CONFIDENCE, JULIO.

40:43.808 --> 40:45.809
I'M GONNA SAY GOOD NIGHT
TO MIKE.

40:55.986 --> 40:57.554
MM.

40:57.556 --> 40:59.956
PER YOUR INSTRUCTIONS,
I'VE DONE A COMPLETE DATA DUMP.

40:59.958 --> 41:02.759
HEY, MIKE, COULD YOU DO ME
A FAVOR...

41:02.761 --> 41:04.727
AND KEEP WHAT I'M ABOUT TO TELL
YOU IN COMPLETE CONFIDENCE?

41:04.729 --> 41:06.162
SURE.

41:06.164 --> 41:10.166
EVEN BRENDA CAN'T KNOW THIS,
ALL RIGHT?

41:10.168 --> 41:14.604
NO KIDDING AROUND.
I GOT TO KNOW I CAN TRUST YOU.

41:14.606 --> 41:16.072
OF COURSE YOU CAN.

41:16.074 --> 41:17.674
I'M TAKING A BACK EXIT.

41:17.676 --> 41:20.076
I NEED YOU
TO MEET ME DOWNSTAIRS

41:20.078 --> 41:21.644
WITH TWO ASPIRIN
AND A BOTTLE OF WATER,

41:21.646 --> 41:23.346
AND THEN I NEED YOU TO DRIVE ME
TO THE HOSPITAL.

41:23.348 --> 41:24.848
WHOA, WHOA, WAIT.
CAN YOU TELL ME WHAT
THE HELL'S GOING ON?

41:24.850 --> 41:26.082
I'M HAVING
A HEART ATTACK.

41:26.084 --> 41:27.484
MEET ME OUT FRONT

41:27.486 --> 41:29.619
AND TAKE ME TO THE E.R.
AT SAINT LUKE'S.

41:29.621 --> 41:32.021
HOLY CRAP.

41:32.023 --> 41:34.591
[ Shakily ] HOLY CRAP.

41:34.593 --> 41:37.660
HOLY CRAP, HOLY CRAP, HOLY...
